               stealing 40 lb. weight of raisins value 10 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17830604-62-victim589" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Butler
                  <interp inst="t17830604-62-victim589" type="surname" value="Butler"></interp>
